oot cause:\n- `javax.xml.parsers.SecuritySupport` is not visible through the normal application class loader on modern JDKs because `javax.xml.parsers` is owned by the JDK `java.xml` module.\n- The test now loads the `xmlParserAPIs` artifact jar through an isolated `URLClassLoader`, so it can reach the artifact’s package-private `javax.xml.parsers.SecuritySupport` class.\n\nUpdated behavior:\n- `getResourceAsStreamUsesProvidedClassLoader()` now loads the artifact class from the actual test classpath jar and invokes the active class method, covering `ClassLoader#getResourceAsStream(String)`.\n- `getResourceAsStreamUsesSystemResourcesWhenClassLoaderIsNull()` invokes the same artifact method with a `null` loader, covering `ClassLoader#getSystemResourceAsStream(String)`.\n- Native Image unsupported dynamic class loading is handled with `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)` as required.\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fb42abf585d89e00169f53e68cdc4819ebb7be26694cb8b32\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1004, "output": 765, "cacheRead": 47616, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 49385, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777679966727, "responseId": "resp_0fb42abf585d89e00169f53e5f4880819ea3345d2f50f85d20"}}
